OL,3,CSurvey reveals one in five shop
OL,4,Cworkers suffered a violent attack in
OL,5,C2023
OL,7,FITV News Reporter Charlie Frost
OL,8,Fexplains the latest findings from the
OL,9,Fretail union Usdaw
OL,11,FShop workers are suffering increased
OL,12,Flevels of violence as customers,
OL,13,Fincluding "hardened career criminals",
OL,14,F, according to new research.
OL,16,Funion Usdaw said a survey of more than
OL,17,F5,500 shop staff showed that almost
OL,18,Fone in five suffered a violent attack
OL,19,Flast year, compared with 8% in 2022.
