OL,7,FUsdaw said the increase in assaults
OL,8,Fcomes during an "epidemic" of retail
OL,9,Fcrime, with official statistics
OL,10,Fshowing significant increases in theft
OL,11,Ffrom shops.
OL,13,FThe union said its study found that in
OL,14,Fthe last year 70% of respondents had
OL,15,Fexperienced verbal abuse, 43% were
OL,16,Fthreatened by a customer and 18% were
OL,17,Fassaulted.
OL,19,FWorker Michelle Whitehead, who has
OL,20,Fbeen in retail for more than 20 years,
OL,21,Fshared her experience with ITV News.
