OL,7,F"A lot of it's for shoplifting -
OL,8,Fthey're coming in, raiding our
OL,9,Fshelves," she said.
OL,11,F"We're asking them to put it back,
OL,12,Fthey're laughing in our faces,
OL,13,Fthreatening us with knives, saying
OL,14,Fthey've got them in their pocket.
OL,16,F"Or they're pushing past us or
OL,17,Fthrowing baskets at us."
