OL,7,FGeneral secretary Paddy Lillis said:
OL,8,F"No-one should feel afraid to go to
OL,9,Fwork, but our evidence shows that too
OL,10,Fmany retail workers are.
OL,12,F"It is shocking that nearly a fifth of
OL,13,Four members working in retail are
OL,14,Fbeing assaulted for simply doing their
OL,15,Fjob and serving the community. They
OL,16,Fprovide an essential service and
OL,17,Fdeserve our respect and the protection
OL,18,Fof the law.
