OL,7,F"Our members have reported that they
OL,8,Fare often faced with hardened career
OL,9,Fcriminals, and we know that retail
OL,10,Fworkers are much more likely to be
OL,11,Fabused by those who are stealing to
OL,12,Fsell goods on.
OL,14,F"Violence and abuse is not an
OL,15,Facceptable part of the job and much
OL,16,Fmore needs to be done to protect shop
OL,17,Fworkers.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
