OL,7,F"The government has repeatedly failed
OL,8,Fto act in the face of an epidemic of
OL,9,Fretail crime, rising theft from shops
OL,10,Fand assaults against retail workers.
OL,11,FIt is disappointing that they have no
OL,12,Fmeasures in their legislative
OL,13,Fprogramme to tackle this issue.
OL,15,F"A protection of shop workers' law is
OL,16,Falso supported by many retailers. It
OL,17,Falready exists in Scotland and has
OL,18,Fsecured over 500 convictions.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
