OL,7,F"We also need more neighbourhood
OL,8,Fpolice, with patrols in town centres,
OL,9,Frespect orders to ban repeat
OL,10,Foffenders, and an end to the #200
OL,11,Fthreshold for investigating and
OL,12,Fprosecuting shop theft.
OL,14,F"Most of all, we ask the public to
OL,15,Fsupport our campaign by respecting
OL,16,Fshop workers."
